style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#7c3aed;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"146\">TUDO O QUE PRECISAS</span>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:42px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:14px;\" data-kid=\"147\">Ferramentas pensadas para<br data-kid=\"148\">o profissional moderno</h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#64748b;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"149\">Cada feature foi desenhada para eliminar atrito e deixar-te focar no que importa: o teu trabalho.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:16px;\" data-kid=\"150\">\n\n      \n      <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:24px;padding:28px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);transition:all .3s;cursor:default;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"151\">\n        <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:120px;height:120px;background:radial-gradient(circle at top right,rgba(99,102,241,0.08),transparent 60%);border-radius:0 24px 0 0;\" data-kid=\"152\"></div>\n        <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff,#c7d2fe);border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"153\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6366f1\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"154\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"4\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\" data-kid=\"155\"></rect><line x1=\"16\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"16\" y2=\"6\" data-kid=\"156\"></line><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"8\" y2=\"6\" data-kid=\"157\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"10\" data-kid=\"158\"></line></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"159\">timebook Calendário</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"160\">Gestão fluida sem colisões de horário para freelancers e estúdios.</p>\n        <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;padding:12px;border-radius:16px;\" data-kid=\"161\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-size:10px;color:#94a3b8;margin-bottom:8px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;\" data-kid=\"162\">\n            <span data-kid=\"163\">Maio 2026</span>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;\" data-kid=\"164\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;background:#7c3aed;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"165\"></span><span style=\"color:#7c3aed;font-weight:600;\" data-kid=\"166\">Ativo</span></div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:4px;\" data-kid=\"167\">\n            <div style=\"padding:5px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;background:#f1f5f9;color:#64748b;border-radius:7px;font-weight:500;\" data-kid=\"168\">25</div>\n            <div style=\"padding:5px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;background:#f1f5f9;color:#64748b;border-radius:7px;font-weight:500;\" data-kid=\"169\">26</div>\n            <div style=\"padding:5px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;background:#7c3aed;color:white;border-radius:7px;font-weight:700;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(124,58,237,0.4);\" data-kid=\"170\">27</div>\n            <div style=\"padding:5px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;background:#eef2ff;color:#6366f1;border-radius:7px;font-weight:600;border:1px solid #c7d2fe;\" data-kid=\"171\">28</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:24px;padding:28px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"172\">\n        <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:120px;height:120px;background:radial-gradient(circle at top right,rgba(16,185,129,0.07),transparent 60%);border-radius:0 24px 0 0;\" data-kid=\"173\"></div>\n        <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d1fae5,#a7f3d0);border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"174\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"175\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\" data-kid=\"176\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\" data-kid=\"177\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\" data-kid=\"178\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\" data-kid=\"179\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"180\">CRM de Clientes</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"181\">Histórico de reservas, notas em cada sessão e dados de contacto centralizados.</p>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;\" data-kid=\"182\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:#f8fafc;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;\" data-kid=\"183\">\n            <div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#7c3aed);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:white;flex-shrink:0;\" data-kid=\"184\">AM</div>\n            <div data-kid=\"185\">\n              <p style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;\" data-kid=\"186\">Ana Martins</p>\n              <p style=\"font-size:10px;color:#22c55e;font-weight:500;\" data-kid=\"187\">✓ Sessão Confirmada</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:#f8fafc;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;\" data-kid=\"188\">\n            <div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c026d3,#9333ea);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:white;flex-shrink:0;\" data-kid=\"189\">BC</div>\n            <div data-kid=\"190\">\n              <p style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;\" data-kid=\"191\">Beatriz Costa</p>\n              <p style=\"font-size:10px;color:#64748b;\" data-kid=\"192\">Hoje às 09:30</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:24px;padding:28px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"193\">\n        <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:120px;height:120px;background:radial-gradient(circle at top right,rgba(14,165,233,0.07),transparent 60%);border-radius:0 24px 0 0;\" data-kid=\"194\"></div>\n        <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e0f2fe,#bae6fd);border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"195\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0ea5e9\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"196\"><rect x=\"5\" y=\"2\" width=\"14\" height=\"20\" rx=\"2\" data-kid=\"197\"></rect><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"12.01\" y2=\"18\" data-kid=\"198\"></line></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"199\">Marcação Fluida</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"200\">Link público personalizado. Os seus clientes agendam em qualquer ecrã com 3 cliques.</p>\n        <div style=\"background:#faf5ff;border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:12px 14px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;\" data-kid=\"201\">\n          <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;color:#6d28d9;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;max-width:140px;\" data-kid=\"202\">timebook.com/lucasdesign</span>\n          <span style=\"font-size:9px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;background:#7c3aed;color:white;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:999px;\" data-kid=\"203\">Ativo</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:24px;padding:28px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"204\">\n        <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:120px;height:120px;background:radial-gradient(circle at top right,rgba(245,158,11,0.07),transparent 60%);border-radius:0 24px 0 0;\" data-kid=\"205\"></div>\n        <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fef3c7,#fde68a);border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"206\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"207\"><polyline points=\"22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17\" data-kid=\"208\"></polyline><polyline points=\"16 7 22 7 22 13\" data-kid=\"209\"></polyline></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"210\">Estatísticas SaaS</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"211\">Acompanhe o crescimento e volume financeiro das suas consultas mensais.</p>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;height:52px;background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;border-radius:14px;padding:8px 12px;\" data-kid=\"212\">\n          <div style=\"width:12px;background:#c4b5fd;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:30%;\" class=\"bar-anim\" data-kid=\"213\"></div>\n          <div style=\"width:12px;background:#a78bfa;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:50%;\" class=\"bar-anim\" data-kid=\"214\"></div>\n          <div style=\"width:12px;background:#7c3aed;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:90%;\" class=\"bar-anim\" data-kid=\"215\"></div>\n          <div style=\"width:12px;background:#22d3ee;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:65%;\" class=\"bar-anim\" data-kid=\"216\"></div>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;\" data-kid=\"217\">\n            <span style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#7c3aed;\" data-kid=\"218\">+90%</span>\n            <span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"219\">Sessões</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:80px auto;padding:0 32px;\" data-kid=\"220\">\n    <div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e1b4b 0%,#312e81 50%,#1e1b4b 100%);border-radius:32px;padding:72px 64px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"221\">\n      \n      <div style=\"position:absolute;top:-60px;right:-60px;width:300px;height:300px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(139,92,246,0.2);pointer-events:none;\" data-kid=\"222\"></div>\n      <div style=\"position:absolute;bottom:-40px;left:-40px;width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(99,102,241,0.15);pointer-events:none;\" data-kid=\"223\"></div>\n\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:52px;\" data-kid=\"224\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#a5b4fc;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"225\">COMO FUNCIONA</span>\n        <h2 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:38px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:white;margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"226\">Em 3 passos simples,<br data-kid=\"227\">a tua agenda está pronta</h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#a5b4fc;max-width:440px;margin:0 auto;\" data-kid=\"228\">Sem instalações. Sem complicações. Começa a receber marcações no mesmo dia.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px;position:relative;\" data-kid=\"229\">\n        \n        <div style=\"position:absolute;top:32px;left:calc(16.66% + 20px);width:calc(66.66% - 40px);height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(165,180,252,0.3),rgba(165,180,252,0.5),rgba(165,180,252,0.3));\" data-kid=\"230\"></div>\n\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;text-align:center;backdrop-filter:blur(12px);\" data-kid=\"231\">\n          <div style=\"width:56px;height:56px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#6366f1);border-radius:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 20px;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:white;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(124,58,237,0.4);\" data-kid=\"232\">1</div>\n          <h4 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:white;margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"233\">Cria a tua conta</h4>\n          <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#c7d2fe;line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"234\">Regista-te em 30 segundos com o teu email profissional. Sem cartão de crédito.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;text-align:center;backdrop-filter:blur(12px);\" data-kid=\"235\">\n          <div style=\"width:56px;height:56px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#6366f1);border-radius:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 20px;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:white;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(124,58,237,0.4);\" data-kid=\"236\">2</div>\n          <h4 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:white;margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"237\">Define a tua agenda</h4>\n          <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#c7d2fe;line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"238\">Configura os teus horários, preços e serviços. O sistema bloqueia automaticamente conflitos.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;text-align:center;backdrop-filter:blur(12px);\" data-kid=\"239\">\n          <div style=\"width:56px;height:56px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#6366f1);border-radius:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 20px;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:white;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(124,58,237,0.4);\" data-kid=\"240\">3</div>\n          <h4 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:white;margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"241\">Partilha o link público</h4>\n          <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#c7d2fe;line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"242\">Os teus clientes agendam diretamente no teu link. Recebem confirmação automática.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:80px auto;padding:0 32px;\" data-kid=\"243\">\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:center;\" data-kid=\"244\">\n      <div data-kid=\"245\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#7c3aed;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"246\">CONSTRUÍDO PARA FLUXO</span>\n        <h2 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:16px;\" data-kid=\"247\">Porque é que profissionais<br data-kid=\"248\">premium escolhem timebook</h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:40px;\" data-kid=\"249\">Diz adeus às trocas infinitas de e-mails para acertar uma data. Foca-te no teu trabalho enquanto a tua agenda trabalha para ti.</p>\n\n        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;\" data-kid=\"250\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;\" data-kid=\"251\">\n            <div style=\"width:42px;height:42px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff,#c7d2fe);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\" data-kid=\"252\">\n              <svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6366f1\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-kid=\"253\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" data-kid=\"254\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\" data-kid=\"255\"></polyline></svg>\n            </div>\n            <div data-kid=\"256\">\n              <h4 style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:4px;\" data-kid=\"257\">Regras de Disponibilidade</h4>\n              <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"258\">Configura as tuas horas ativas de trabalho e o sistema garante que ninguém reserva fora disso.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;\" data-kid=\"259\">\n            <div style=\"width:42px;height:42px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#cffafe,#a5f3fc);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\" data-kid=\"260\">\n              <svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0891b2\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-kid=\"261\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\" data-kid=\"262\"></path></svg>\n            </div>\n            <div data-kid=\"263\">\n              <h4 style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:4px;\" data-kid=\"264\">Prevenção Contra Conflitos</h4>\n              <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"265\">Sincronização imediata. Um horário agendado fica instantaneamente bloqueado para outros clientes.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;\" data-kid=\"266\">\n            <div style=\"width:42px;height:42px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fef3c7,#fde68a);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\" data-kid=\"267\">\n              <svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"2\" data-kid=\"268\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\" data-kid=\"269\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\" data-kid=\"270\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\" data-kid=\"271\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\" data-kid=\"272\"></path></svg>\n            </div>\n            <div data-kid=\"273\">\n              <h4 style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:4px;\" data-kid=\"274\">Painel Multi-dispositivo</h4>\n              <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"275\">Gere marcações no telemóvel ou no PC. Design totalmente fluído preparado para toque ou clique.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;\" data-kid=\"276\">\n        <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:20px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\" data-kid=\"277\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;\" data-kid=\"278\">\n            <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/44?u=ana_martins\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;\" alt=\"Ana Martins\" data-kid=\"279\">\n            <div data-kid=\"280\">\n              <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;\" data-kid=\"281\">Ana Martins</p>\n              <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#64748b;\" data-kid=\"282\">Psicóloga Clínica · Lisboa</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-left:auto;color:#f59e0b;font-size:14px;\" data-kid=\"283\">★★★★★</div>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;\" data-kid=\"284\">\"Reduzi o tempo que passava a gerir marcações em 80%. O timebook é indispensável no meu consultório.\"</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#6366f1);border-radius:20px;padding:24px;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(124,58,237,0.25);\" data-kid=\"285\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;\" data-kid=\"286\">\n            <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/44?u=miguel_ferreira\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\" alt=\"Miguel Ferreira\" data-kid=\"287\">\n            <div data-kid=\"288\">\n              <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:white;\" data-kid=\"289\">Miguel Ferreira</p>\n              <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);\" data-kid=\"290\">Personal Trainer · Porto</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-left:auto;color:#fde68a;font-size:14px;\" data-kid=\"291\">★★★★★</div>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;\" data-kid=\"292\">\"Os meus clientes adoram a facilidade de agendar. Nunca mais tive um double-booking. Perfeito.\"</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"background:white;border-radius:20px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #f1f5f9;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\" data-kid=\"293\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;\" data-kid=\"294\">\n            <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/44?u=sofia_costa\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;\" alt=\"Sofia Costa\" data-kid=\"295\">\n            <div data-kid=\"296\">\n              <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;\" data-kid=\"297\">Sofia Costa</p>\n              <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#64748b;\" data-kid=\"298\">Designer Freelancer · Remote</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-left:auto;color:#f59e0b;font-size:14px;\" data-kid=\"299\">★★★★★</div>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;\" data-kid=\"300\">\"Interface simples, poderosa e bonita. Recomendo a qualquer freelancer que queira profissionalizar a sua agenda.\"</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:80px auto 0;padding:0 32px;\" data-kid=\"301\">\n    <div style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f5f3ff 0%,#ede9fe 50%,#ddd6fe 100%);border-radius:32px;padding:80px 64px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #c4b5fd;\" data-kid=\"302\">\n      \n      <div style=\"position:absolute;top:-80px;left:-80px;width:300px;height:300px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(124,58,237,0.1);pointer-events:none;\" data-kid=\"303\"></div>\n      <div style=\"position:absolute;bottom:-60px;right:-60px;width:260px;height:260px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(99,102,241,0.1);pointer-events:none;\" data-kid=\"304\"></div>\n\n      <div style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;\" data-kid=\"305\">\n        <div style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:white;border:1px solid #ddd6fe;padding:6px 18px;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:24px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(124,58,237,0.1);\" data-kid=\"306\">\n          <span style=\"width:7px;height:7px;background:#7c3aed;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"307\"></span>\n          <span style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#6d28d9;\" data-kid=\"308\">Começa grátis hoje</span>\n        </div>\n        <h2 style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:46px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-2px;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:16px;\" data-kid=\"309\">Pronto para transformar<br data-kid=\"310\">a tua agenda?</h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#4c1d95;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 40px;line-height:1.6;opacity:0.75;\" data-kid=\"311\">Junta-te a mais de 1.200 profissionais que já automatizaram as suas marcações com o timebook.</p>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;\" data-kid=\"312\">\n          <button style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#6366f1);color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:14px;border:none;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(124,58,237,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\" data-kid=\"313\">\n            Criar Agenda Grátis\n            <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" data-kid=\"314\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\" data-kid=\"315\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\" data-kid=\"316\"></polyline></svg>\n          </button>\n          <button style=\"background:white;color:#6d28d9;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #ddd6fe;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\" data-kid=\"317\">Ver Demo ao Vivo</button>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7c3aed;margin-top:16px;opacity:0.7;\" data-kid=\"318\">Sem cartão de crédito · Cancela quando quiseres</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 32px 32px;\" data-kid=\"319\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding-bottom:24px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"320\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"321\">\n        <div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#6366f1);border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\" data-kid=\"322\">\n          <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"323\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"4\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" rx=\"2\" data-kid=\"324\"></rect><line x1=\"16\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"16\" y2=\"6\" data-kid=\"325\"></line><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"8\" y2=\"6\" data-kid=\"326\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"10\" data-kid=\"327\"></line></svg>\n        </div>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;\" data-kid=\"328\">timebook</span>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:28px;\" data-kid=\"329\">\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;\" data-kid=\"330\">Produtos</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;\" data-kid=\"331\">Funcionalidades</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;\" data-kid=\"332\">Preços</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;\" data-kid=\"333\">Blog</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\